):

1. *Dobre* je da se trudim da postignem svoje ciljeve. (It is good that I am trying to achieve my goals.)

2. On je *dobro* razumeo situaciju. (He understood the situation well.)

3. *Dobri* ljudi su retki. (Good people are rare.)

4. *Dobro* se igraju ovakve igre. (These games are fun to play.)

5. Ona je izabrala *dobru* karijeru. (She chose a good career.)

6. Svi smo *dobri* u nečemu. (We are all good at something.)

7. Ona je *dobro* razumela moje riječi. (She understood my words well.)

8. *Dobro* je da smo došli na vrijeme. (It is good that we arrived on time.)